das in the same way that a grid does:\r\n\r\ne.g\r\n```\r\nclass Parent\r\n{\r\n   Child child;\r\n}\r\n\r\nclass Child\r\n{\r\nString name;\r\n}\r\n\r\nBinder<Parent> binder;\r\n\r\nbinder.bind(parent -> parent.child.name);\r\n```\r\nThis form will allow for code refactoring without breakage and make it consistent with Grid column binding.\r\n\r\n","score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vaadin/framework/issues/10699","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vaadin/framework","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vaadin/framework/issues/10699/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vaadin/framework/issues/10699/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vaadin/framework/issues/10699/events","html_url":"https://github.com/vaadin/framework/issues/10699","id":303855245,"number":10699,"title":"Grid columns reordering does not behave correctly when grid is empty","user":{"login":"margus80","id":37216313,"avatar_url":"https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/37216313?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/margus80","html_url":"https://github.com/margus80","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/margus80/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/margus80/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/margus80/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/margus80/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/margus80/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/margus80/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/margus80/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/margus80/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/margus80/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":842702960,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vaadin/framework/labels/BFP","name":"BFP","color":"E00040","default":false},{"id":16896444,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vaadi